      • getExceptionStackTrace

        String getExceptionStackTrace()
        Returns:
        exception stack trace. It can be null if no exception has been thrown or a query has not been executed with QueryOption.resultWithException option enabled.

      • getParameters

        Map<String,String> getParameters()
        Returns:
        method invocation parameters. It can be null if there are no parameters or a query has not been executed with QueryOption.resultWithParameters option enabled.
